    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 122034.0,
      "end_time": 123450.0,
      "text": "The statement of cash flows can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 123450.0,
      "end_time": 126240.0,
      "text": "prepared using the direct or indirect method."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 126240.0,
      "end_time": 129600.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s quickly look at the differences before we move on."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 129600.0,
      "end_time": 132390.0,
      "text": "The direct method lists the inflows and outflows"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 132390.0,
      "end_time": 135950.0,
      "text": "from each type of operating activity a company performs."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 135950.0,
      "end_time": 139990.0,
      "text": "Cash flow categories can include cash collected from customers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 139990.0,
      "end_time": 142920.0,
      "text": "cash paid to suppliers, and cash paid to employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 142920.0,
      "end_time": 144510.0,
      "text": "just to list a few."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 144510.0,
      "end_time": 147630.0,
      "text": "This method is preferred by IFRS because it"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 147630.0,
      "end_time": 150900.0,
      "text": "is more informative for users, clearly showing the sources"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 150900.0,
      "end_time": 153420.0,
      "text": "and uses of cash in operations."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 153420.0,
      "end_time": 155760.0,
      "text": "The indirect method focuses on the differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 155760.0,
      "end_time": 158730.0,
      "text": "between net income under accrual accounting and cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 158730.0,
      "end_time": 161220.0,
      "text": "from operations under cash accounting."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 161220.0,
      "end_time": 165090.0,
      "text": "It starts with net income and adjusts for non-cash items."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 165090.0,
      "end_time": 167160.0,
      "text": "The direct method is more difficult for users"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 167160.0,
      "end_time": 170880.0,
      "text": "to understand, but it does not stop approximately 98%"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 170880.0,
      "end_time": 173850.0,
      "text": "of all US, European, and Canadian companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173850.0,
      "end_time": 176550.0,
      "text": "from using the indirect method to calculate cash flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176550.0,
      "end_time": 179220.0,
      "text": "from operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 179220.0,
      "end_time": 180720.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 180720.0,
      "end_time": 183990.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s easier and less costly to prepare."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 183990.0,
      "end_time": 187110.0,
      "text": "One benefit for users of the indirect method"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187110.0,
      "end_time": 189840.0,
      "text": "is that it highlights earnings management."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 189840.0,
      "end_time": 191284.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll further explore this concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 191284.0,
      "end_time": 193200.0,
      "text": "when we cover the development of the cash flow"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 193200.0,
      "end_time": 195517.0,
      "text": "statements in a later video."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 195517.0,
      "end_time": 197850.0,
      "text": "As you can imagine, we&#39;ll be using the statement of cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 197850.0,
      "end_time": 202027.0,
      "text": "flows indirect method for purposes of all of our videos."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202027.0,
      "end_time": 203610.0,
      "text": "The statement of cash flows is divided"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 203610.0,
      "end_time": 206320.0,
      "text": "into three activities, operating, investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206320.0,
      "end_time": 207510.0,
      "text": "and financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 207510.0,
      "end_time": 209400.0,
      "text": "Description of these activities have already"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 209400.0,
      "end_time": 210870.0,
      "text": "been covered in a previous video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 210870.0,
      "end_time": 213140.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s just review them."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 213140.0,
      "end_time": 215960.0,
      "text": "Financing is activities that fund a company either"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 215960.0,
      "end_time": 218150.0,
      "text": "through debt or equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218150.0,
      "end_time": 220940.0,
      "text": "Investing is activities that result from buying or selling"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 220940.0,
      "end_time": 224480.0,
      "text": "property, plant, equipment, intangibles, or investments"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 224480.0,
      "end_time": 226890.0,
      "text": "in other corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 226890.0,
      "end_time": 230130.0,
      "text": "Operating activities is when a company does their business"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 230130.0,
      "end_time": 234030.0,
      "text": "day-to-day, selling and delivering goods or services."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 234030.0,
      "end_time": 235710.0,
      "text": "To obtain an in-depth understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 235710.0,
      "end_time": 237900.0,
      "text": "of these activities, please see my video"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 237900.0,
      "end_time": 239940.0,
      "text": "on business activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 239940.0,
      "end_time": 243200.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do a quick check of your understanding so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 243200.0,
      "end_time": 245570.0,
      "text": "The payment of interest on a long term loan"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 245570.0,
      "end_time": 253280.0,
      "text": "is considered either an operating or financing"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 253280.0,
      "end_time": 254330.0,
      "text": "activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254330.0,
      "end_time": 256610.0,
      "text": "IFRS allows prepares to choose where"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 256610.0,
      "end_time": 258320.0,
      "text": "to place interest payments."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 258320.0,
      "end_time": 260720.0,
      "text": "The reason why will be explored in future videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 260720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264259.0,
      "text": "on developing a statement of cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 264259.0,
      "end_time": 265800.0,
      "text": "Now that we understand the activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 265800.0,
      "end_time": 268870.0,
      "text": "that make up the statement, we can look at an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 268870.0,
      "end_time": 271290.0,
      "text": "Note that the statement is so large that I&#39;ve divided it"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 271290.0,
      "end_time": 274500.0,
      "text": "into two slides so that you can see each activity better."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 274500.0,
      "end_time": 277072.0,
      "text": "But the statement is actually one statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 277072.0,
      "end_time": 279030.0,
      "text": "Although I have set up the statement in columns"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 279030.0,
      "end_time": 281160.0,
      "text": "for easy viewing, the accounts can all"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 281160.0,
      "end_time": 286320.0,
      "text": "be listed in one column and the amounts in another."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 286320.0,
      "end_time": 288940.0,
      "text": "As always, the statement starts with a heading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 288940.0,
      "end_time": 290920.0,
      "text": "which must include the company name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 290920.0,
      "end_time": 292590.0,
      "text": "the title of the financial statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 292590.0,
      "end_time": 294330.0,
      "text": "and the period of time covered."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 294330.0,
      "end_time": 298050.0,
      "text": "Note, similar to every financial statement except the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 298050.0,
      "end_time": 300390.0,
      "text": "of financial position, this statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 300390.0,
      "end_time": 303930.0,
      "text": "is for a period of time, most commonly, one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 303930.0,
      "end_time": 305790.0,
      "text": "Note that profit from the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 305790.0,
      "end_time": 308760.0,
      "text": "is the beginning point under the indirect method."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 308760.0,
      "end_time": 310590.0,
      "text": "All the other amounts are reconciling"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 310590.0,
      "end_time": 313620.0,
      "text": "items between profit from the income statement and cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 313620.0,
      "end_time": 316060.0,
      "text": "flow from operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 316060.0,
      "end_time": 318210.0,
      "text": "This includes things such as depreciation"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 318210.0,
      "end_time": 320670.0,
      "text": "and the change in current asset and liability accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 320670.0,
      "end_time": 322920.0,
      "text": "from the statement of financial position."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 322920.0,
      "end_time": 324450.0,
      "text": "At the bottom of this section, we"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 324450.0,
      "end_time": 327300.0,
      "text": "see that operating activities resulted in a net cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 327300.0,
      "end_time": 330990.0,
      "text": "inflow of $21,400."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 330990.0,
      "end_time": 332910.0,
      "text": "Investing activities are next."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 332910.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll note, there is a net cash outflow of $7,500."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 340680.0,
      "text": "This is due to the purchase of both equipment and investments."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 340680.0,
      "end_time": 343320.0,
      "text": "Finally, let&#39;s look at financing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 343320.0,
      "end_time": 345600.0,
      "text": "Some of the items under financing activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 345600.0,
      "end_time": 348540.0,
      "text": "have a connection to the statement of changes in equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 348540.0,
      "end_time": 351690.0,
      "text": "Here, we see that the company issued shares as well as"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 351690.0,
      "end_time": 353610.0,
      "text": "repurchased some."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 353610.0,
      "end_time": 355560.0,
      "text": "They also paid dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 355560.0,
      "end_time": 358380.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s quickly flip back to the statement of changes in equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 358380.0,
      "end_time": 360677.0,
      "text": "so we can see the relationship."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 360677.0,
      "end_time": 362760.0,
      "text": "Both the statement of cash flows and the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 362760.0,
      "end_time": 367050.0,
      "text": "of changes in equity show a dividend payment of $2,500."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 367050.0,
      "end_time": 369540.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because this amount was paid in cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 369540.0,
      "end_time": 371460.0,
      "text": "In addition, both statements show"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 371460.0,
      "end_time": 375100.0,
      "text": "an issue of shares of $11,600."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 375100.0,
      "end_time": 378570.0,
      "text": "Again, that&#39;s because this amount was received in cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 378570.0,
      "end_time": 380760.0,
      "text": "Note that the repurchase of shares on the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 380760.0,
      "end_time": 383310.0,
      "text": "of changes in equity is $5,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 383310.0,
      "end_time": 387990.0,
      "text": "But the outflow on the statement of cash flows was $7,500."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 387990.0,
      "end_time": 391560.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because the $5,000 is historical cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 391560.0,
      "end_time": 395970.0,
      "text": "and the $7,500 on the statement of cash flows was cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 395970.0,
      "end_time": 398550.0,
      "text": "Further discussions of why these two amounts are different"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 398550.0,
      "end_time": 400920.0,
      "text": "will be covered in a future video."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 400920.0,
      "end_time": 403500.0,
      "text": "Looking at the total from the financing activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 403500.0,
      "end_time": 408349.0,
      "text": "we can see there was a net outflow of $1,700."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 408349.0,
      "end_time": 409890.0,
      "text": "The bottom of the cash flow statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 409890.0,
      "end_time": 411990.0,
      "text": "shows a net change in cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 411990.0,
      "end_time": 414780.0,
      "text": "This is a summation of all three activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 414780.0,
      "end_time": 418230.0,
      "text": "operating inflow of $21,400, investing"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 418230.0,
      "end_time": 424170.0,
      "text": "and financing outflows of $7,500, respectively."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 424170.0,
      "end_time": 429000.0,
      "text": "The net increase in cash was therefore $12,200."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 429000.0,
      "end_time": 433110.0,
      "text": "Add this to the beginning cash balance of $72,300"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 433110.0,
      "end_time": 437190.0,
      "text": "and we get the ending cash balance of $84,500."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 437190.0,
      "end_time": 439890.0,
      "text": "This amount is a cash balance on the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 439890.0,
      "end_time": 442620.0,
      "text": "of financial position under current assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 442620.0,
      "end_time": 444690.0,
      "text": "Again, this is the interconnection"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 444690.0,
      "end_time": 446610.0,
      "text": "between the statement of financial position"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 446610.0,
      "end_time": 449150.0,
      "text": "and the statement of cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 449150.0,
      "end_time": 452120.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a quick look at the statement of cash flow again."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 452120.0,
      "end_time": 454640.0,
      "text": "Remember we start with the appropriate heading and profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 454640.0,
      "end_time": 456050.0,
      "text": "from the income statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 456050.0,
      "end_time": 458630.0,
      "text": "We move on to the operating activities and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 458630.0,
      "end_time": 461270.0,
      "text": "the investing activities, with the financing activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 461270.0,
      "end_time": 462590.0,
      "text": "listed last."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 462590.0,
      "end_time": 465200.0,
      "text": "The net change in cash is then added--"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 465200.0,
      "end_time": 468620.0,
      "text": "this is when a net inflow is demonstrated, as it is here--"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 468620.0,
      "end_time": 472520.0,
      "text": "or deducted, if there is a net outflow from the opening cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 472520.0,
      "end_time": 475490.0,
      "text": "balance to obtain the closing cash balance from the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 475490.0,
      "end_time": 478590.0,
      "text": "of financial position."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 478590.0,
      "end_time": 480850.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s check your understanding for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 480850.0,
      "end_time": 483240.0,
      "text": "Remember to pause the video to determine your own answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 483240.0,
      "end_time": 485660.0,
      "text": "before continuing."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 485660.0,
      "end_time": 488330.0,
      "text": "The president of Greene Corp. announces the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 488330.0,
      "end_time": 490430.0,
      "text": "is expanding into new markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 490430.0,
      "end_time": 492230.0,
      "text": "You examine the statement of cash flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 492230.0,
      "end_time": 496220.0,
      "text": "and see a net cash outflow from operating activities and inflow"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 496220.0,
      "end_time": 499280.0,
      "text": "from both investing and financing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 499280.0,
      "end_time": 501200.0,
      "text": "Does the statement of cash flows support"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 501200.0,
      "end_time": 502620.0,
      "text": "the president&#39;s announcement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 507580.0,
      "end_time": 508150.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 508150.0,
      "end_time": 510120.0,
      "text": "No, it does not."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 510120.0,
      "end_time": 513100.0,
      "text": "A net outflow from operating activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 513100.0,
      "end_time": 516220.0,
      "text": "means cash outflows are greater than inflows."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 516220.0,
      "end_time": 519280.0,
      "text": "Since operating activities are the only sustainable source"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 519280.0,
      "end_time": 522760.0,
      "text": "of cash, this does not support expansion plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 522760.0,
      "end_time": 525700.0,
      "text": "In addition, an inflow from investing activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 525700.0,
      "end_time": 527980.0,
      "text": "means the company is selling assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 527980.0,
      "end_time": 532860.0,
      "text": "not buying assets necessary to expand into new markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 532860.0,
      "end_time": 536730.0,
      "text": "So what questions does the statement of cash flow answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 536730.0,
      "end_time": 538890.0,
      "text": "For investors, it helps them determine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 538890.0,
      "end_time": 540690.0,
      "text": "in conjunction with the income statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 540690.0,
      "end_time": 544050.0,
      "text": "if there will be enough cash in the future to pay dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 544050.0,
      "end_time": 545820.0,
      "text": "For lenders and other creditors, it"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 545820.0,
      "end_time": 548760.0,
      "text": "helps them determine if there is cash available to pay debts"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 548760.0,
      "end_time": 550290.0,
      "text": "as they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 550290.0,
      "end_time": 552510.0,
      "text": "It also helps them determine if the company will"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 552510.0,
      "end_time": 555280.0,
      "text": "need further financing in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 555280.0,
      "end_time": 558510.0,
      "text": "Finally, all external users can use the cash flow statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 558510.0,
      "end_time": 562937.0,
      "text": "with the income statement to help predict future cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 562937.0,
      "end_time": 565020.0,
      "text": "We have now completed all the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 565020.0,
      "end_time": 566250.0,
      "text": "under IFRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 566250.0,
      "end_time": 567690.0,
      "text": "But there is an important addition"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 567690.0,
      "end_time": 569190.0,
      "text": "to the statements, which we have not"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 569190.0,
      "end_time": 571050.0,
      "text": "covered, the notes that accompany"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 571050.0,
      "end_time": 572520.0,
      "text": "the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 572520.0,
      "end_time": 575940.0,
      "text": "And that will be the topic of our next video."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 575940.0,
      "end_time": 578690.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    }
  ]
}